(D.G., unpubl.). fflis explanation also seems less convincing than the one involving courtship because the extent of the male secondary sexual characters in
Dichaetophora ancora
is limited almost entirely to the small “mandibles,” and combat using these structures would be difficult since the flies are hypognathous, not prognathous.
